 href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/mandela-online-application-form\/#Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_MANDELA\" title=\"Applying for Financial Assistance in MANDELA\">Applying for Financial Assistance in MANDELA<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/mandela-online-application-form\/#Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_MANDELA_Admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for MANDELA Admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for MANDELA Admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80650724\">About the Nelson Mandela University (MANDELA) Online Application Form 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80650725\"><strong>How to Apply for MANDELA Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80650726\">Documents Required for MANDELA Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80650727\">MANDELA Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80650728\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80650729\">Applying for Financial Assistance in MANDELA<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80650730\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for MANDELA Admission 2024?<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-nelson-mandela-university-mandela-online-application-form-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_Nelson_Mandela_University_MANDELA_Online_Application_Form_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80650724\"><\/a>About the Nelson Mandela University (MANDELA) Online Application Form 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the Nelson Mandela University(MANDELA) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80650725\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for MANDELA Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4 id=\"%c2%b7-visit-here\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%C2%B7_Visit_here\"><\/span>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/applyonline.mandela.ac.za\/home.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-mandela-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_MANDELA_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80650726\"><\/a>Documents Required for MANDELA Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/applyonline.mandela.ac.za\/requireddocuments.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view other required documents<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"mandela-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MANDELA_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80650727\"><\/a>MANDELA Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee of R100 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R100<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80650728\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30\u00a0September 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-mandela\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_MANDELA\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80650729\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in MANDELA<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application <a href=\"http:\/\/www.nsfas.org.za\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">portal<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/applyonline.mandela.ac.za\/home.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-mandela-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_MANDELA_Admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80650730\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for MANDELA Admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"MANDELA Online Application Form 2024 for Admission into Nelson Mandela University, MANDELA Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1134,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1133"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/commen